overview: The funny man, the man who has given us so many Good Times and Great Memories, he is Colt Cabana and this is a chronicle of his journey in Ring of Honor. Whether it be standing alongside CM Punk & Ace Steel as a Second City Saint, or running solo in pursuit of champion ship success, Cabana has proven himself a master of the art of pro wrestling.
title: Colt Cabana: Chicago's Favorite Son
